							<binding>
								<p>BM/BL in-house. Black buckram, blind-tooled.</p>
								<p>Spine title: 'Midrash on Numbers. Hebrew. Brit. Mus. Oriental 1490.'</p>
							</binding>
						</bindingDesc>
